at|

It is objectionable because more often than not you are helping to develop a long suit in the declarer's hand and at the same time giving him a clear picture of the whole suit. |
pg| ***** 9 ***** |


at|

There are times when the singleton lead is ideal. The conditions are as follows:|
pg| ***** 10 ***** |


at|

^c(1)You hold a sure trump trick. |
pg| ***** 11 ***** |


at|

