pg| ***** 12 ***** |


at|

If however, you have a sure trump trick you can regain the lead early in the play and proceed to lead into your partner's hand to obtain the ruff or at least cash whatever tricks you can. |
pg| ***** 13 ***** |


nt|^B@2^Z@3In other words, when you hold a sure trump trick the declarer cannot "run away with the hand."|
